<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>

<title>Result - CE Amplifier</title>

<style>

body {
    font-family: Arial;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #e3f2fd, #ffffff);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 100px;
}

h1 {
    color: #0d47a1;
    animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in;
}

p {
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #333;
    opacity: 0;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
    from {opacity: 0;}
    to {opacity: 1;}
}

.show {
    animation: slideUp 2s forwards;
}

@keyframes slideUp {
    from {
        transform: translateY(40px);
        opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
        transform: translateY(0px);
        opacity: 1;
    }
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<h1>Result</h1>

<p id="line1">
Frequency response of the CE amplifier was obtained successfully.
</p>

<p id="line2">
Voltage gain is maximum in the mid-frequency region.
</p>

<p id="line3">
Lower Cutoff Frequency (fL) = 120 Hz
</p>

<p id="line4">
Upper Cutoff Frequency (fH) = 85 kHz
</p>

<p id="line5">
Bandwidth (BW) = 84.88 kHz
</p>

<script>

setTimeout(() => {
document.getElementById("line1").classList.add("show");
}, 1000);

setTimeout(() => {
document.getElementById("line2").classList.add("show");
}, 2500);